                            <li>Dimm­aktor 4-fach LED (380-625&nbsp;€)</li>
                            <li>Schalt­aktor 8-fach (235-340&nbsp;€)</li>
                            <li>Optional: KNX-Konstant­lichtregler &amp; DALI-Gateway</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="knx-uc-price">
